title: V.A  analogkid6103's  Now That's Music (8-CD) 2015 320ak
description:
V.A  analogkid6103's  Now That's Music (8-CD) 2015 320


My 101 track playlist I started this list on Sept.10 2015 and finished Oct. 22 2015
I think it will be a satisfactory playlist. 
I have listened to it a few times.  In cd form it takes minimum of 8 CD's.  
There are only 3 or 4 artists repeated.   Otherwise its a long playing trip all through the late 70's to 2015. 
If you like tell me, I like making these. And I will make more of em.

These are a mix of tracks I have enjoyed alot the last few years. And 
some much longer. Anyway enough of my talk...
